WEBVTT

00:00:00.240 --> 00:00:05.119
Hey, good morning family. Praise the Lord. Thank you for joining me today.

00:00:05.120 --> 00:00:20.959
Well, we got an article somebody sent us talking about Iran threatening our military if Trump strikes Iran, that there would be retaliations against our bases overseas.

00:00:20.960 --> 00:00:45.835
So, I was like, "This is exactly what the Lord showed me in prayer to y'all when we were praying to pray for Iraq and the military base in Iraq, that I saw drones flying in and dropping stuff out of them and hurting our troops."That we would pray for a supernatural hedge of protection around our troops.

00:00:45.836 --> 00:01:01.558
So whenever Iran immediately threatened our military bases, I thought, "Wow, this is what the Lord was showing us."And so we're going to keep continual prayer over our military men and women that are serving our country.

00:01:01.559 --> 00:01:14.245
Then the Lord was showing me Trump was trying to devise a plan to strike Iran and that it would be through Israel. And so he had three different plan options.

00:01:14.246 --> 00:01:24.329
And it was like I said in the spirit when I was looking in the spirit, it was like chess trying to think ahead strategically.

00:01:24.330 --> 00:01:29.190
"If we do this what will they do? If we do this what will they do?

00:01:29.191 --> 00:01:41.999
And how will we do this?"And so the Lord showed me when I was praying last night, I was praying over strategic battle plans that Trump would have the wisdom to know what to do.

00:01:42.000 --> 00:01:53.695
Praying over him to have the wisdom to know what to do. Praying over him to have foresight to see way in the future of knowing this is what's going to be the retaliation of this, you know.

00:01:53.696 --> 00:02:08.038
And right now I know being diplomatic is what he's doing. "Hey, you all stop this or we're going to do this."So, he's not going to go right in and just guns blazing without having some diplomacy is what I'm trying to say.

00:02:08.039 --> 00:02:17.455
There has to be some kind of diplomacy. So, right now we're seeing diplomacy because he has to justify what he's going to do to all the other nations of the world.

00:02:17.456 --> 00:02:35.515
"Hey, we're going to stop Iran from having a nuclear weapon in the Middle East."A nuclear Iran is a bad Iran, and really, bottom line, I believe they probably already have one, but you have to go about it this way because it's more tactful.

00:02:35.516 --> 00:02:38.636
So, that's what we're seeing right now. We're seeing it in the news.

00:02:38.637 --> 00:02:46.697
Everything the Lord showed us clear back before he was inaugurated, we're seeing it in the news today.

00:02:46.698 --> 00:02:55.576
So we see Trump saying things on Truth Social, and so he is saying that on the second they're going to implement these tariffs.

00:02:55.577 --> 00:03:04.811
So we need to pray over the economy. I know what the Lord showed me about a major economic crash.

00:03:04.812 --> 00:03:13.627
I know what he told me about this. I've told you this this time last year. I've told you this for a while now.

00:03:13.628 --> 00:03:26.226
But I know what the Lord showed me about October in the intercessory prayer that we did as a nation, praying and asking God to delay what was coming.

00:03:26.227 --> 00:03:37.611
I don't believe it stopped. I believe we delayed it. And that's what I'm praying about: keeping the line strong, having a rectangular window of opportunity.

00:03:37.612 --> 00:03:46.031
It looked like a rectangle whenever I was looking over in it, to believe for the wealth of the sinner laid up for the righteous.

00:03:46.032 --> 00:03:58.038
I told you there's hard days coming. I told you there's a great shaking to awaken, and I believe we're seeing the birthing pains of that right now.

00:03:58.039 --> 00:04:05.199
We see all the things of him trying to make America great. Folks, it was a mess.

00:04:05.200 --> 00:04:13.723
This was a catastrophic mess of what the Biden and Harris administration had and where we were going.

00:04:13.724 --> 00:04:19.618
If she would have won, I'm telling you, we would be in a totally different ballgame right now.

00:04:19.619 --> 00:04:26.696
But I believe with God's grace, we're having a window of opportunity to fix some things.

00:04:26.697 --> 00:04:36.997
Now, is it too far gone to fix? Only God knows. But we see the things happening. But I'm believing for a window.

00:04:36.998 --> 00:04:51.939
I'm believing for a window for the wealth of the sinner laid up for the righteous, for the remnant to have enough finances to take and be able to do the gospel in a major way for what I've seen coming.

00:04:51.940 --> 00:05:00.083
I'm talking disasters. I'm praying over another EMP attack that I've seen that I've not talked about a lot because people get all freaked out about it.

00:05:00.084 --> 00:05:08.973
But I'm telling you, I've seen some dark things. And the Lord has told me, "Brandon, there is a humbling coming to America.

00:05:08.974 --> 00:05:16.399
There's a great shaking coming to America."I told you about the heart and the black of the heart upon the land.

00:05:16.400 --> 00:05:18.979
And there was a little sliver, and I believe that's the remnant.

00:05:18.980 --> 00:05:33.034
I believe that's the people like you and me praying and interceding for this nation, and that there was a sliver of red and all this other when the hearts were collected combined, it was all black.

00:05:33.035 --> 00:05:38.511
And the further it went out, the darker it got. And this is another thing.

00:05:38.512 --> 00:05:47.958
After the word the Lord gave us last night when we were praying, he showed me a major cleaning of the house again.

00:05:47.959 --> 00:05:55.152
And I'm telling y'all, I could feel the Lord's—it wasn't anger.

00:05:55.153 --> 00:06:03.354
It was correction for sure of the churches not taking their authority, preaching the gospel like they should.

00:06:03.355 --> 00:06:12.834
And he said, "Brandon, you're being too kind, basically saying that the church is lukewarm in these areas."He said, "It's not lukewarm.

00:06:12.835 --> 00:06:17.403
They're cold."And they're feeding the people a cold, stale bread.

00:06:17.404 --> 00:06:21.831
Basically, the bread of affliction, just keeping them alive.

00:06:21.832 --> 00:06:28.759
You know, it's like the prisoners when you don't want to feed them too much, you don't want them to die, but you just keep them alive.

00:06:28.760 --> 00:06:38.895
You know, whenever in bad war times, you don't want to give them enough strength to fight you, but they are there just to sustain life.

00:06:38.896 --> 00:06:42.984
And that's what's happening with a lot of churches from what I saw in the spirit.

00:06:42.985 --> 00:06:47.679
And he even brought it up from Maine all the way down to Pennsylvania and all that.

00:06:47.680 --> 00:06:55.483
I saw it in the vision and the Lord showed me, he said, "These people are from every denomination, tribe, and tongue.

00:06:55.484 --> 00:07:03.860
They are not teaching the people how to stand and live by faith."And I'm thankful a lot of you all are here.

00:07:03.861 --> 00:07:12.496
I hope this channel has brought you hope. I pray that we're giving you that meat that you're getting fed here.

00:07:12.497 --> 00:07:21.266
I thought when I went to Florida and we were driving through all those areas, I thought there has to be an oasis somewhere.

00:07:21.267 --> 00:07:32.517
There has to be that oasis that people can go and drink from the well, drink and get filled up by the Holy Ghost every single day.

00:07:32.518 --> 00:07:43.020
And I know you can do that on your own personal times, but I hope that you can get that here, that Diana and I, we and the kids, we're praying for you.

00:07:43.021 --> 00:07:51.194
We believe that God is still on the throne. And it's like Billy Burke said, "Brandon, you've always got to bring hope.

00:07:51.195 --> 00:08:00.230
Hope to the people. Yeah, you deliver the hard words, but always bring hope. Tell the people there's hope."And I believe there's hope.

00:08:00.231 --> 00:08:05.380
Just like what he was telling me, and I believe that, and God bless him, I love Billy Burke.

00:08:05.381 --> 00:08:10.478
He is a friend and I am thankful for him. But I'm telling you all, there is hope there.

00:08:10.479 --> 00:08:15.425
It's not all doom and gloom. It is not a time of just going "the sky's falling,"Chicken Little.

00:08:15.426 --> 00:08:20.397
This is a time of rejoicing because our redemption is drawing nigh.

00:08:20.398 --> 00:08:26.947
And I believe with all my heart, we're about to see the greatest harvest of souls this world has ever seen.

00:08:26.948 --> 00:08:33.547
And all the darkness and all the things that I'm telling you that if you stay horizontal, it can affect you.

00:08:33.548 --> 00:08:38.585
But if we keep vertical, it won't. And I'm telling you, I'm believing God. I'm believing God for big.

00:08:38.586 --> 00:08:59.393
I'm believing God for a big 2025 in this cleaning of the house, of the exposing of the wickedness and doing the things that I've seen happening with the church preparing itself for this great, great move of God, birthing us out of prayer and getting ready for this major revival that's about to take place.

00:08:59.394 --> 00:09:03.788
I still believe for the supernatural wealth transfer to take place.

00:09:03.789 --> 00:09:12.805
I'm not letting that go. We need it. My family needs it. We need it for what God has told us to do, for what I know is coming.

00:09:12.806 --> 00:09:18.398
It's going to take major finances to do it. And so we're just stretching out there.

00:09:18.399 --> 00:09:22.672
It's like the Lord said, 'Stretch forth your net to Peter,'whenever he was there.

00:09:22.673 --> 00:09:30.310
And he said, 'Lord, I've been fishing all night. I'm exhausted. I'm ready to go home.'That is basically what he was saying.

00:09:30.311 --> 00:09:41.434
But Jesus said, 'Just trust me,'and he threw the net over on the side one more time and he got the biggest bumper crop he could ever hope or imagine or think.

00:09:41.435 --> 00:09:48.669
And he's the 'exceedingly abundantly above all that we dare ask or think'God. And we believe—that's the way that Diana and I believe.

00:09:48.670 --> 00:09:54.504
We're believing for exceedingly abundantly above all that we dare ask or think. I'm talking for major things.

00:09:54.505 --> 00:10:03.914
I don't get into it all on this YouTube channel to tell you what we're believing for because I don't want doubt and unbelief trying to hinder what I'm believing for.

00:10:03.915 --> 00:10:11.584
I have to keep my eyes vertical. And if I tell people what I'm believing for, they're going to go, 'What?'and it's a chokehold for me.

00:10:11.585 --> 00:10:16.813
So I don't need everybody speaking their doubt into what I'm believing for.

00:10:16.814 --> 00:10:26.149
I just keep things to myself and we keep things as a family, and we're just believing for big because I know what God has told us to do.

00:10:26.150 --> 00:10:33.048
It's going to be an international ministry and someway, somehow, I know that the Lord is calling us to do something huge.

00:10:33.049 --> 00:10:39.754
And even like the lady—I don't know who you were, but you sent Diana a really nice black purse last night.

00:10:39.755 --> 00:10:48.719
I polished that black purse up, and she got a pair of nice sandals that needed cleaning up; a lady just gave them to my wife.

00:10:48.720 --> 00:10:53.679
So I was just taking the Magic Eraser and cleaning things up.

00:10:53.680 --> 00:10:58.221
It's a blessing when people send you stuff and they try to be nice to you.

00:10:58.222 --> 00:11:10.188
I told Diana, 'We don't know who it is, but boy, your people just try to love on you.'They gave her a black purse, a coat, and stuff, and put it in a box to bless my wife last night.

00:11:10.189 --> 00:11:22.559
She was so excited to get those sandals. I said, 'Baby, let me clean them up for you and get that leather cleaned up and make it look nice.'We're just so grateful for people doing things like that for us.

00:11:22.560 --> 00:11:28.304
You don't have to, but whenever somebody just does something out of the kindness of their heart, you just want to say thank you.

00:11:28.305 --> 00:11:36.315
And Diana was just thankful. She sat there and said, 'You know, Brandon, I was praying for some sandals for the summer.'Isn't that amazing?

00:11:36.316 --> 00:11:40.719
And what was even more amazing, folks, is they were her size.

00:11:40.720 --> 00:11:47.439
Nobody knows what size of shoe my wife wears, but God put it on this lady's heart to send her shoes.

00:11:47.440 --> 00:11:55.456
I thought, 'What a kindness!'So things like that blessed us.

00:11:55.457 --> 00:12:03.645
I took those shoes and I polished and cleaned them all up for her last night and got them all ready. She said, 'Thanks, baby.'It's just a blessing.

00:12:03.646 --> 00:12:10.836
I got the purse all cleaned up, put that leather cleaner on there, and polished that leather up until it smelled like brand new leather.

00:12:10.837 --> 00:12:23.359
I thought, 'What a blessing.'So we're just grateful. But I just wanted to tell whoever that was—you've never emailed before and there was no way to contact you to tell you thank you.

00:12:23.360 --> 00:12:28.083
So God bless you and know that we pray for you to have a great harvest.

00:12:28.084 --> 00:12:38.048
Diana said, 'Let's pray for her to have some leather purses back there.'Blessings in everything.

00:12:38.049 --> 00:12:49.599
Like I said, you all, we are in Central Oklahoma, and all the areas of Oklahoma, Kansas, Texas, and Missouri get major tornadoes.

00:12:49.600 --> 00:12:55.933
I've told you I've seen major tornadoes, but you have authority over tornadoes.

00:12:55.934 --> 00:13:07.119
You as believers need to pray, not being afraid of tornado season in America or wherever you're at.

00:13:07.120 --> 00:13:12.669
You have authority to pray and take authority over the storms.

00:13:12.670 --> 00:13:25.787
When the weatherman comes on and says, 'Hey, there's going to be golf-ball-sized hail, there's going to be baseball-sized hail, and it's going to come with 50-mile-per-hour winds that will break out windows and everything,'start praying in the spirit.

00:13:25.788 --> 00:13:36.016
Take authority over the storms, telling them, 'No, you will not do this over our house. You will not have destruction over our house.

00:13:36.017 --> 00:13:47.177
We bind this demonic storm and we tell you to cease and desist in your maneuvering,'just like Jesus did when he said, 'Peace, be still'to the storm.

00:13:47.178 --> 00:13:54.381
We are created in the image of God and we are joint heirs of Jesus Christ; and as he is, so are we in this world.

00:13:54.382 --> 00:14:05.430
Say that: 'As he is, so are we in this world.'And we take authority over that storm in the name of Jesus.

00:14:05.431 --> 00:14:15.680
We tell you to have peace, be still. And you'll see that storm as we're praying. You can see that storm part and it starts to fall apart.

00:14:15.681 --> 00:14:19.269
And all of a sudden, they'll have a tornado, 'Well, we just lost it.'And it's so funny.

00:14:19.270 --> 00:14:28.571
We laugh about it because we see the weatherman doing his best to try to tell us what's going on, but we're over there praying and binding and telling the storm to die.

00:14:28.572 --> 00:14:33.893
You can see it on the radar on the TV; that thing just falls apart.

00:14:33.894 --> 00:14:40.876
I believe every believer has that authority to tread on serpents and scorpions, and nothing shall by any means hurt you.

00:14:40.877 --> 00:14:52.163
I believe with all my heart that we have authority over the storms—not just spiritual storms, but physical storms, mental storms, whatever storm is trying to come against you.

00:14:52.164 --> 00:14:57.260
You have authority over the storm. I believe you should use your authority.

00:14:57.261 --> 00:15:03.278
Don't shy away from it. Call it. Speak to it. Say, 'No.'And then pray for the rain.

00:15:03.279 --> 00:15:11.339
Say, 'Thank you, Father, for rain. Rain's a blessing.'You know, we have authority to call in the rain. Call in the low-pressure system.

00:15:11.340 --> 00:15:24.774
Say, 'Bring in the rain from the Gulf of America now.'Whatever we're going to call it, the Gulf of America, 'Bring forth the rain in Jesus'name.'And Father, we thank you, Lord, for the supernatural rain so that we don't have drought.

00:15:24.775 --> 00:15:32.236
We call forth rain—two or three inches of rain—and we say in the name of Jesus, drought's broken.

00:15:32.237 --> 00:15:41.439
We will not have this. You have to speak to your weather. We have dominion and authority just like Adam.

00:15:41.440 --> 00:15:51.233
Adam spoke and God gave Adam dominion over all the birds and all the fish and over all the animals.

00:15:51.234 --> 00:15:55.531
He gave us dominion over the earth, over the air, over all of it.

00:15:55.532 --> 00:16:01.570
You have to realize that you have that power and authority. If Jesus did it, we can do it.

00:16:01.571 --> 00:16:07.251
As he is, so are we in this world. That's what the Bible says. And I believe it.

00:16:07.252 --> 00:16:13.128
So you just need to know that because we're in storm season and they're already forecasting big storms tomorrow.

00:16:13.129 --> 00:16:20.958
I said, 'No, we ain't going to have no big storm tomorrow. We're not going to have no high winds.

00:16:20.959 --> 00:16:33.698
We're not going to have major hail these things.'Over my area, over where I live, and where I put the tread of my soles, we're going to have peace over the weather.

00:16:33.699 --> 00:16:39.953
We're just going to have good rain. You just got to start saying that and believing it. You've got to believe it.

00:16:39.954 --> 00:16:44.978
You've got to put it in your heart and say it out of your mouth: 'I have authority over the storms.

00:16:44.979 --> 00:16:50.879
I have authority over the rain. I have authority over the clouds. I have authority over the sun.'I pray over it.

00:16:50.880 --> 00:17:00.285
If Joshua could delay the sun and do what he did and cause it to stand still.

00:17:00.286 --> 00:17:04.168
He was in the Old Covenant. Could God do that again for us if we needed it?

00:17:04.169 --> 00:17:10.838
I'm not saying we can just make the sun stand still all the time, but if we needed it, could God do it again?

00:17:10.839 --> 00:17:23.263
Yes. We're talking about the sun standing still. How much more could we call for some clouds? I see the cloud the size of a man's hand.

00:17:23.264 --> 00:17:40.157
If Elijah could cause the rain not to fall for three years because he prayed earnestly and interceded on behalf of the drought—telling it to be a drought and no rain to come—how much more could we do it?

00:17:40.158 --> 00:17:45.293
I don't want drought, but I'm calling for rain to come. That's what I'm talking about.

00:17:45.294 --> 00:17:51.613
We need rain. We need our lakes to be full, our ponds to be full, and our grass to be green.

00:17:51.614 --> 00:17:59.977
Throughout the summer, we call for cooler temperatures. We aren't going to roast in 120 degrees; we're going to have cooler temperatures.

00:17:59.978 --> 00:18:10.591
I call cold fronts in from Canada, in the name of Jesus. Share some of that cold air, Canada.

00:18:10.592 --> 00:18:17.189
We call the cold air down in Jesus'name. That's what I tell them all summer: 'Share the air.

00:18:17.190 --> 00:18:22.569
You've got to share some of that air down here in the South; it's hot.'We've got to have some colder air down here.

00:18:22.570 --> 00:18:28.314
So, just keep remembering: as He is, so are you in this world.

00:18:28.315 --> 00:18:35.956
He said that greater works we would do. Everything Jesus did, we can do.

00:18:35.957 --> 00:18:52.458
Just remember that we are joint heirs with Him. Be thankful for that dominion and authority today. Be thankful for what He's doing in your life.

00:18:52.459 --> 00:18:59.058
We can speak to the mountain: 'Be thou removed and be thou cast into the sea.'And if you shall not doubt in your heart, you shall have whatsoever things you say.

00:18:59.059 --> 00:19:07.478
I believe that we're blessed in the city, blessed in the field, blessed coming in, and blessed going out.

00:19:07.479 --> 00:19:11.953
I believe that we're the head and not the tail, above and not beneath.

00:19:11.954 --> 00:19:22.243
You've got to believe it. Well, I'm a believing believer; that's why I say that all the time.

00:19:22.244 --> 00:19:32.075
I'm not a doubter. I'm an overcomer by the blood of the Lamb and by the word of my testimony.

00:19:32.076 --> 00:19:44.159
I'm a believing believer who has authority and victory, walking in victory.

00:19:44.160 --> 00:19:56.530
I'm not just barely getting by; I have overflow. I can do all things through Christ who strengthens me.

00:19:56.531 --> 00:20:06.845
I believe it, I receive it, and I'll walk in it. I will not be a child who is barely getting by while the devil's running me over.

00:20:06.846 --> 00:20:20.167
I'm going to run over him. Why? Because greater is He that is in me than he that is in the world.

00:20:20.168 --> 00:20:25.599
There's not a devil in hell that can trample over you; we trample over them.

00:20:25.600 --> 00:20:37.257
He said, 'I give you power and authority to trample over all serpents and scorpions, and nothing shall by any means hurt you.'I believe it.

00:20:37.258 --> 00:20:40.908
The devil comes as a roaring lion seeking whom he may devour.

00:20:40.909 --> 00:20:52.083
He isn't devouring me, my wife, or my children. No weapon formed against me shall prosper. A curse without a cause cannot stand.

00:20:52.084 --> 00:20:58.034
There are all kinds of witches trying to do stuff, but a curse without a cause cannot stand.

00:20:58.035 --> 00:21:02.481
There's no cause there. I haven't opened any doors; I keep my doors shut.

00:21:02.482 --> 00:21:09.524
We take communion. No weapon formed against you will prosper.

00:21:09.525 --> 00:21:15.759
Greater is He that is in you than he that is in the world. You have dominion and authority.

00:21:15.760 --> 00:21:24.008
Take your communion right now. It's real; it's the meal that heals.

00:21:24.009 --> 00:21:32.558
It gives you power and authority to do all these things because it represents a covenant.

00:21:32.559 --> 00:21:39.183
Jesus'blood paid the price for you to have a covenant. I have a covenant with God.

00:21:39.184 --> 00:21:51.625
It's like a marriage covenant. When you put the ring on, I'm in covenant with her and she's in covenant with me.

00:21:51.626 --> 00:22:03.524
That's why we say 'for richer or poor, until death do us part.'Those are covenant remarks.

00:22:03.525 --> 00:22:19.745
I'm going to be with her until death do us part, for richer or poor—though I don't believe for 'poor'; I believe for 'richer or richer.'We've walked through the valley of being poor, but I'm going out on the other side.

00:22:19.746 --> 00:22:29.666
I'm not going to live there; I'm not camping there. Some people are campers; they sit down and say, 'I'm going to just live here.'No, I'm not living in poverty.

00:22:29.667 --> 00:22:37.799
I'm getting a four-wheel drive vehicle and moving on through.

00:22:37.800 --> 00:22:47.746
I believe that's part of the covenant. Everything is about covenant.

00:22:47.747 --> 00:22:53.673
There's so much covenant in our society that we don't even realize.

00:22:53.674 --> 00:23:02.493
It's covenant language. It 'sticks out like a sore thumb.'That came from covenant. Why does it stick out like a sore thumb?

00:23:02.494 --> 00:23:08.794
Because they used to cut the thumb and mingle the blood—blood brothers and things like that.

00:23:08.795 --> 00:23:14.693
You ought to study where the origin of that came from. It comes from covenant talk. Why does it stick out?

00:23:14.694 --> 00:23:22.809
Because they made the sore thumb as part of the covenant; they cut it, and it looks like a sore because they mingle blood and you become blood brothers.

00:23:22.810 --> 00:23:35.714
But with those chieftains and all, that all happens. There's so much covenant stuff people don't realize.

00:23:35.715 --> 00:23:49.279
One day I'll study that more and I'll teach it to you all because I want to get it perfect.

00:23:49.280 --> 00:23:58.573
I'm going to make sure I get this down pat. But what I'm telling you now is real.

00:23:58.574 --> 00:24:11.465
I know what I'm talking about. God gave us a covenant with His Son's blood.

00:24:11.466 --> 00:24:23.015
As He is, so are we in this world. Everything He has is mine, and all that I have is His.

00:24:23.016 --> 00:24:27.833
He gave His life to me; I gave my life to Him. We're in covenant.

00:24:27.834 --> 00:24:44.214
He said that I'm a joint heir with Jesus Christ. I was adopted. Praise God, I am His and He is mine.

00:24:44.215 --> 00:24:52.558
Everything He did on that cross—He said, 'By my stripes, you were healed.'I am healed because of Him.

00:24:52.559 --> 00:25:00.855
